sources.title: One Body Too Many
sources.description: 1944 directed by Frank McDonald starring Jack Haley, Jean Parker, Bela Lugosi, Lyle Talbot, Blanche Yurka, Douglas Fowley, Fay Helm, Lucien Littlefield, Dorothy Granger and Maxine Fife. Tepid insurance agent Albert Tuttle, (Jack Haley), decides to keep a month-old appointment with a millionaire unaware that the man has died and his seedy relatives are gathered at his mansion for the reading of his will.
